OL,3,CChinese man's home surrounded by
OL,4,Cmotorway after rejecting compensation
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FA man in China had a highway built
OL,8,Faround his home after he regrettably
OL,9,Fturned down a relocation package worth
OL,10,Fnearly #200,000.
OL,12,FHuang Ping lives in a two-storey house
OL,13,Fin the eastern county of Jinxi with
OL,14,Fhis 11-year-old grandson. He now
OL,15,Fspends his days in the town centre to
OL,16,Favoid the nearby construction site,
OL,17,Fonly returning once the workers have
OL,18,Fgone.
