OL,3,CChinese man's home surrounded by
OL,4,Cmotorway after rejecting compensation
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FHe reportedly says it feels as if he
OL,8,Fhas "lost a big bet," as his home is
OL,9,Fnow level with the constructed
OL,10,Fmotorway, surrounded by dust and
OL,11,Foccasionally shakes from the ongoing
OL,12,Fworks.
OL,14,F"If I could turn back time, I would
OL,15,Fagree to the demolition conditions
OL,16,Fthey offered... Now it feels like I
OL,17,Flost a big bet," he said.
OL,19,F"I regret it a bit."
