OL,7,FHuang's home has become an attraction
OL,8,Ffor locals with videos shared on
OL,9,FChinese social media. Pictures from
OL,10,FDouyin
OL,12,FThe motorway has not opened yet, but
OL,13,FHuang fears how he will live once it
OL,14,Fdoes.
OL,16,FHuang decided to stay after he was
OL,17,Foffered #178,245 and two other
OL,18,Fproperties by the local government.
