OL,4,Cmotorway after rejecting compensation
OL,5,Coffer
OL,7,FThe secretary of the Jinxi County
OL,8,FParty Committee previously said Huang
OL,9,Frefused to relocate as he was
OL,10,Fdissatisfied with the government's
OL,11,Foffer.
OL,13,FLocals now visit his home to take
OL,14,Fphotos of the house surrounded by
OL,15,Fconstruction.
OL,17,FIn China, it is common for the
OL,18,Fgovernment to build around homes,
OL,19,Fknown as dingzhius or nail houses,
OL,20,Fwhen owners refuse to move.
