OL,7,FThese homes are seen as symbols of the
OL,8,Fstruggle between people and the
OL,9,Fauthorities, as well as the conflict
OL,10,Fbetween tradition and progress.
OL,12,FHomeowners of nail houses often risk
OL,13,Fhaving their properties demolished.
